Results.ReviewText: I have been buying Nescafe Original for over 25 years and the latest improvement to the blend makes it by far the best ever.  I look forward to my first cup through to my last cup of the day.
Results.Title: Wonderful way to wake up in the mrning

Results.ReviewText: I have tried many different makes of coffee, but the best for my family and I is Nescafe original!!  The best looking, smelling and tasting coffee, anytime of day or night!  Simply the best!!
Results.Title: Great Taste!

Results.ReviewText: Have tried many brands of coffee over the years, including store own brands. Always come back to Nescafe for its quality and smoothness. Also buy the instant sachets for convenience at work.
Results.Title: Delish

Results.ReviewText: I have loved Nescafe original for many years - tried others but always come back to Nescafe. Recently discovered the refill bags - perfect - always fresh - would never use anything else now.
Results.Title: Always hits the spot.

Results.ReviewText: You can keep all your expensive coffees and coffee houses-nothing beats the taste of nescafe original especially first thing in the mirning. My only problem is that I want to drink too much!
Results.Title: Awakening!

Results.ReviewText: I think Nescafe red cap coffee is mellow compared to the brown cap original, i have allways been a heavy Nescafe coffee drinker,and the new coffee lacks the full flavour of the true Original
Results.Title: still just a ok coffee

Results.ReviewText: excellent coffee, really hits the spot first thing in the morning and keeps on doing so throughout the day . the smell is great , especially openeing a new jar . wouldnt buy any other coffee
Results.Title: love the smell of new jar

Results.ReviewText: I buy this regularly - its a great instant coffee with a great taste.   I often buy at a special offer price at my local supermarket.   Always reliable.   I alternate this with Nescafe Gold.
Results.Title: Good Yesterday, today and tomorrow

Results.ReviewText:
I have been using Nescafé since it first came on the market a long time ago nnnow
The product has done nothing but improve over the years and can't be beaten for flavour or value for money
Results.Title: Greatest instant coffee granules on the market

Results.ReviewText: I have been drinking Nescafé Original for many, many years and never buy anything else it is a lovely drink. I have found a difference in the taste since the jar lid colour changed to red.
Results.Title: Great features

Results.ReviewText: I have been drinking this coffee for years and my children keep some at their homes for when I visit. I never drink tea and this suits my needs to drink all day and I drink a lot of coffee
Results.Title: Best coffee ever

Results.ReviewText:
I only buy Nescafé Original, and in bulk when it's on offer.
I have tried other coffee's at work or at friends, and they don't come close to the taste of a freshly opened jar of Nescafé.
Results.Title: No other coffee comes close.

Results.ReviewText: The are many ways to drink your coffee these days, hot, cold, black, weak, strong, milk, cream, skinny, fat etc. only you need is a jar of  Nescafe original and invite your friends round
Results.Title: Versatility

Results.ReviewText:
I have nescafe original every morning and i must say coiuldn't start the day without it!!
No other coffee ive had has that deep rich full flavour of nescafe, it sets me up for the day!
Results.Title: Early morning must!

Results.ReviewText: Always buy Nescafe and didn't think it could get any better but when the original came out I was surprised as its smoother, with more flavour and gets the thumbs up from me and my gang!

This is now my preferred coffee , just love the aroma and taste of filter coffee without the messing .
I have had visitors say how much they have enjoyed the coffee  so it has a 10/10
Results.Title: amazing aroma and taste

Results.ReviewText: Can't remember when I first drank Nescafe Original (I'm now 76) but nothing can beat it. Not sure it has improved recently but so what. Try the others and yuo'll soon revert to Nescafe
Results.Title: Simply The Best

Results.ReviewText: Always bought this product for as long as I can remember as its the best, have tried loads of other products using nescafe as my marker to judge others, so far there is nothing better.
Results.Title: well worth the money

Results.ReviewText: Proper coffee from the moment the aroma is released from the jar. Ready quickly and easily but at no cost to the quality and flavour. Let Nescafe do the work, so I can enjoy the perk!
Results.Title: Proper coffee

Results.ReviewText: I purchased my Nescafe Original refill pouch 2 weeks ago. You just cannot beat the aroma when you open the pouch & the taste of this coffee matches up to aroma. Wonder taste & smell.
Results.Title: Nescafe Original - the 1st & best

Results.ReviewText: I only drink black coffee and it's my first drink of the day - has to be good quality to get the taste right and other brands just don't cut it!  Can't be without my Nescafe Original
Results.Title: The Only One

Results.ReviewText: I am over seventy years old and have had Nescafe original every day, obviously there is no guarantee your coffee enables longevity but the juxtaposition may not just be a coincidence
Results.Title: Always reliable, always satisfying.

Results.ReviewText: I have been drinking Nescafe original for years. I like the refill option. It's easy to refill a Nescafe jar. It is a greener option and that must be good for the rest of the world.
Results.Title: Great taste

Results.ReviewText: I love the taste of this coffee, I will never swap it for anything else, I remembered it in my kitchen as a child, bring a lot of good memories and it will make lots more I am sure.
Results.Title: Nescafe original

Results.ReviewText: Having tried many other brands of coffee, I still keep coming back to Nescafé Original, it's full coffee flavour is my absolute favourite, never bitter, just a great tasting coffee.
Results.Title: The best tasting Nescafe

Results.ReviewText: We used to send a catering tin of Nescafe powder to my grandmother in Italy every Christmas. She knew her coffee and passed her knowledge to me - nothing else has ever come near it!
Results.Title: Memories that have stood the test of time

Results.ReviewText: Every time I buy Nescafé the flavour is always reliable, excellent tasty coffee first time every time. Good value for money and of the highest quality, I never buy any other coffee.
Results.Title: Flavour never alters

Results.ReviewText: After  a few months of trying other coffee's I have, for the last 6 weeks, been back on Nescafe Original.  Always was and always will be the best Instant coffee around.  I love it.
Results.Title: Wonderful taste and smell

Results.ReviewText: delicious and easy coffee to make for busy  working mornings.Bold without too much bitterness . perfect with milk and sugar. I also use this for my renowned coffee and walnut cakes
Results.Title: lovely flavour!
